  "title": "Locum / Perm Speech therapist (Office Hours) #HGA",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assess and treat speech, language, communication, and swallowing disorders.</li><li>Develop and implement personalized therapy plans for children and/or adults</li><li>Provide guidance and training to caregivers and educators.</li><li>Work collaboratively with healthcare teams to support patient goals.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Speech-Language Pathology or equivalent.</li><li>Licensed or certified by the relevant professional board.</li><li>Excellent communication and observation skills.</li><li>Prior experience in clinical, school, or community settings is beneficial</li><li>For locum roles, min 2 - 3 days per week!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>If you are interested in any of the positions, do kindly drop your most updated resume to anngoh@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Ann Goh Xin Ting</p><p>EA Personnel No: R1875289</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)</p><p>EA License: 99C4599</p>",
